WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 16=

01:45.980 --> 01:46.930
Miss Cai,

01:47.980 --> 01:49.260
the Young Master isn't with you?

01:49.900 --> 01:51.770
He's been locking himself in his room.

01:52.930 --> 01:53.850
The Young Master...

01:58.020 --> 01:59.180
What happened to him?

01:59.620 --> 02:00.833
What did his mother do to him?

02:02.020 --> 02:03.180
He didn't ask me to tell you.

02:03.290 --> 02:05.490
He didn't ask you
not to tell me, either.

02:07.130 --> 02:08.290
If you won't tell me,

02:08.290 --> 02:09.290
I'll go ask Xing.

02:09.940 --> 02:10.780
Wait.

02:13.850 --> 02:15.260
It's not that she did something.

02:15.260 --> 02:16.850
It's that she did nothing.

02:17.660 --> 02:18.736
Unworthy of being a mother.

02:18.883 --> 02:19.880
Back then, Nie Hengcheng,

02:19.890 --> 02:22.043
to control the Young Lord,
the Young Master's father,

02:22.054 --> 02:22.923
kept sending beauties

02:22.934 --> 02:24.260
into the Young Lord's chambers.

02:24.260 --> 02:25.510
But the Young Lord was upright

02:25.510 --> 02:26.540
and rejected them all.

02:26.540 --> 02:28.060
Only Sun Ruoshui,

02:28.400 --> 02:29.730
the daughter of his master,

02:30.010 --> 02:31.370
kept saying

02:32.060 --> 02:33.690
she had nowhere to go.

02:33.690 --> 02:34.940
He softened for a moment

02:34.940 --> 02:36.010
and took her in.

02:36.010 --> 02:37.290
But after she gained his favor,

02:37.290 --> 02:38.780
she got involved

02:38.780 --> 02:40.570
with Nie Zhe as well.

02:42.850 --> 02:44.010
Playing both sides?

02:44.010 --> 02:44.980
Exactly.

02:45.340 --> 02:46.610
How despicable.

02:47.940 --> 02:48.820
Here.

02:48.820 --> 02:49.660
Wet your throat.

02:54.500 --> 02:55.686
There's something even worse.

02:56.060 --> 02:57.340
Sun Ruoshui,

02:57.340 --> 02:58.690
to please Nie Zhe,

02:58.690 --> 02:59.540
actually claimed

02:59.540 --> 03:00.410
that the Young Master

03:00.410 --> 03:01.980
was Nie Zhe's son.

03:01.980 --> 03:03.130
Isn't that outrageous?

03:04.060 --> 03:07.130
She trampled the Young Lord's dignity.

03:09.170 --> 03:11.730
Even worse than the stories in novels.

03:12.260 --> 03:13.690
The Young Lord was so poor.

03:15.260 --> 03:16.570
Everyone said

03:16.570 --> 03:18.170
his wife cheated on him.

03:23.160 --> 03:24.010
Fortunately,

03:24.010 --> 03:25.410
heaven has eyes.

03:25.410 --> 03:26.530
As the Young Master grew up,

03:26.743 --> 03:27.999
he looked like his real father.

03:28.010 --> 03:28.890
They looked

03:28.890 --> 03:30.780
very much alike.

03:31.380 --> 03:33.260
Only then did those rumors fade away.

03:33.260 --> 03:34.100
So,

03:34.410 --> 03:35.380
the Young Master

03:35.820 --> 03:37.410
is truly the Young Lord's son.

03:41.890 --> 03:42.940
Guanyue,

03:43.220 --> 03:44.660
we're just talking here.

03:45.610 --> 03:46.780
Can you stop forcing tears?

03:46.780 --> 03:47.690
It looks fake.

03:48.340 --> 03:49.980
This is all genuine emotion.

03:51.130 --> 03:52.100
Don't fool me.

03:52.500 --> 03:53.890
I grew up watching operas.

03:54.220 --> 03:55.170
Your acting is far worse

03:55.570 --> 03:57.610
than the Young Master's mother.

04:02.890 --> 04:04.130
Speak of the devil.

04:04.726 --> 04:06.126
We shouldn't have talked about her.

04:10.260 --> 04:11.380
Greetings, Lady Sun.

04:11.380 --> 04:13.730
You have deep insight into operas.

04:14.380 --> 04:16.540
A refined soul indeed.

04:16.540 --> 04:17.380
You flatter me.

04:17.700 --> 04:19.220
Lady Sun, your life is like a play.

04:19.426 --> 04:20.730
You're quite fascinating as well.

04:32.220 --> 04:34.900
Your room is truly unique

04:35.250 --> 04:36.250
in its arrangement.

04:36.490 --> 04:37.370
Much better

04:37.370 --> 04:39.290
than my quarters.

04:39.290 --> 04:40.980
Qingyan truly takes

04:40.980 --> 04:42.780
good care of you.

04:42.780 --> 04:44.250
After all, I never abandoned him.

04:45.490 --> 04:46.330
Lady Sun, please.

04:49.660 --> 04:52.410
Every mother loves her son.

04:53.370 --> 04:55.100
But I'm a weak woman,

04:55.780 --> 04:57.290
strictly watched by Nie Zhe,

04:57.900 --> 04:59.220
with limited freedom.

05:00.100 --> 05:01.780
I truly had no choice.

05:03.700 --> 05:04.700
I understand.

05:05.900 --> 05:08.370
Yet when Mu Qingyan was
about to attack Bliss Palace,

05:09.020 --> 05:10.660
you conveniently regained your freedom.

05:11.250 --> 05:13.170
Nie Zhe is so considerate.

05:19.340 --> 05:20.180
Please have some tea.

05:31.220 --> 05:32.060
Miss Cai,

05:33.020 --> 05:34.410
we're on the same side.

05:34.730 --> 05:36.050
Why be so distant?

05:36.780 --> 05:37.810
I heard

05:37.810 --> 05:39.410
you're Cai Pingshu's niece.

05:39.930 --> 05:41.100
With your help,

05:41.100 --> 05:42.220
Qingyan is truly fortunate.

05:42.930 --> 05:43.770
However,

05:44.220 --> 05:45.540
I'm very curious.

05:46.700 --> 05:48.250
Why are you willing to help him?

05:48.850 --> 05:49.780
Is there

05:50.220 --> 05:52.340
some unknown connection

05:52.340 --> 05:54.340
between Qingyan and the Six Sects?

05:56.140 --> 05:57.140
As for connections,

05:58.540 --> 05:59.380
there are none.

05:59.580 --> 06:00.580
But following my aunt,

06:00.980 --> 06:02.410
I've always loved to right wrongs

06:02.410 --> 06:03.900
and uphold justice,

06:03.900 --> 06:05.140
especially when I see someone

06:05.140 --> 06:06.810
bullied by their own mother.

06:09.220 --> 06:10.610
Please drink your tea.

06:18.850 --> 06:19.980
Miss Cai,

06:20.580 --> 06:22.340
join me for this cup.

06:32.250 --> 06:33.490
What exactly

06:33.490 --> 06:34.540
are you here for?

06:35.340 --> 06:37.730
There's no outcome between Nie Zhe
and Mu Qingyan yet.

06:38.100 --> 06:40.050
Who will control the sect
is still uncertain.

06:40.980 --> 06:43.220
For you to place your bet so early

06:43.980 --> 06:45.810
isn't that a bit too eager?

06:46.050 --> 06:47.660
Why misunderstand me so?

06:47.980 --> 06:49.900
I truly want to help Qingyan.

06:50.250 --> 06:51.340
Your suspicion

06:52.660 --> 06:54.250
really breaks my heart.

06:56.370 --> 06:57.900
How discourteous of me.

06:59.050 --> 07:01.660
Since you harbor
so many doubts about me,

07:02.140 --> 07:03.660
I shouldn't linger here.

07:04.020 --> 07:04.930
Given time,

07:05.490 --> 07:07.250
true intentions will be revealed.

07:25.250 --> 07:26.090
Sleeping drug.

07:29.100 --> 07:30.810
Poor acting, and childish.

07:31.697 --> 07:33.390
Luckily, Mu Qingyan
didn't take after her.

07:34.020 --> 07:34.860
Laxative?

07:35.410 --> 07:37.370
Where did Mu Qingyan find
such a vile woman?

08:12.780 --> 08:13.980
What are you doing here?

08:14.490 --> 08:15.410
I can't sleep.

08:15.850 --> 08:16.700
If you can't sleep,

08:17.660 --> 08:19.730
go read or practice martial arts.

08:20.100 --> 08:21.370
Or at worst, go perform a ritual.

08:21.780 --> 08:23.050
Why come bother me?

08:24.580 --> 08:26.020
I couldn't sleep,

08:26.020 --> 08:27.490
so I wanted to chat with you,

08:27.490 --> 08:28.930
but you were sleeping so soundly

08:28.930 --> 08:30.170
that I didn't dare disturb you.

08:30.170 --> 08:31.410
So, I lay down beside you

08:32.130 --> 08:33.420
and waited for you to wake up.

08:33.420 --> 08:35.610
Mu Qingyan, are you even human?

08:36.420 --> 08:37.260
Compared to you,

08:37.940 --> 08:39.370
those lechers killed by my aunt

08:39.370 --> 08:41.340
were wrongly accused.

08:46.700 --> 08:48.250
You've read so many stories.

08:49.250 --> 08:52.370
Would those lechers

08:52.370 --> 08:53.850
who sneak into a lady's room at night

08:54.370 --> 08:55.340
lie there like me,

08:56.060 --> 08:57.940
doing nothing at all?

08:59.130 --> 08:59.980
Stay away from me.

09:08.300 --> 09:10.130
You even brought a pillow?

09:11.010 --> 09:11.850
Of course.

09:12.250 --> 09:14.100
Doesn't that prove even more

09:14.100 --> 09:15.940
that I'm not here
to do anything improper?

09:16.220 --> 09:17.060
How so?

09:17.580 --> 09:19.250
If I truly wanted to misbehave,

09:20.060 --> 09:21.250
one pillow would be enough.

09:22.220 --> 09:22.926
Besides,

09:22.986 --> 09:25.206
I'm afraid you might harbor
improper thoughts about me.

09:25.580 --> 09:26.650
You...

09:26.650 --> 09:27.580
You're talking nonsense.

09:29.060 --> 09:30.220
Say what you need to say.

09:30.650 --> 09:31.490
Then leave.

09:32.610 --> 09:33.940
I suddenly don't know what to say.

09:35.220 --> 09:36.130
Zhao, you go first.

09:37.580 --> 09:39.300
I went to see your mother yesterday.

09:40.510 --> 09:41.450
What did you talk about?

09:42.130 --> 09:43.650
She wanted to give me something.

09:44.300 --> 09:45.850
I wanted to give her something too.

09:45.850 --> 09:46.730
Give something?

09:48.220 --> 09:49.013
What?

09:49.106 --> 09:50.232
She gave me a sleeping drug.

09:50.650 --> 09:51.770
I gave her a laxative.

09:54.770 --> 09:55.940
In this whole world,

09:56.730 --> 09:58.250
only you would deal with her like that.

09:58.940 --> 10:00.610
Your father was such a detached man.

10:01.250 --> 10:02.820
Why did he fall for her?

10:09.773 --> 10:11.300
She was my father's master's daughter.

10:12.850 --> 10:14.370
Nie Hengcheng brought her to him.

10:14.890 --> 10:15.820
He knew my father

10:17.130 --> 10:17.970
would soften

10:18.370 --> 10:19.650
and take her in.

10:21.420 --> 10:22.770
She was good at endurance.

10:23.700 --> 10:25.010
She stayed for five or six years,

10:26.130 --> 10:27.300
only discussing poetry,

10:28.980 --> 10:30.060
never overstepping.

10:31.610 --> 10:32.530
Over time,

10:33.770 --> 10:34.890
feelings naturally grew.

10:35.610 --> 10:36.530
Five or six years.

10:37.980 --> 10:39.820
Nie Hengcheng was quite patient.

10:40.180 --> 10:41.610
Nie Hengcheng excelled at schemes.

10:43.010 --> 10:44.530
If he wanted something done,

10:45.130 --> 10:46.250
he would wait for 10 years,

10:46.980 --> 10:48.250
or even 20 years.

10:49.983 --> 10:51.530
He longed for sole control of the sect

10:52.220 --> 10:53.580
but feared public condemnation.

10:54.610 --> 10:55.530
He never truly killed

10:56.100 --> 10:57.770
the Mu clan descendants.

10:58.340 --> 10:59.700
Instead, he manipulated them

11:00.730 --> 11:02.580
and made them like puppets.

11:04.250 --> 11:05.250
Through marriage,

11:05.332 --> 11:06.789
he plotted against my grandparents,

11:06.861 --> 11:08.720
turning them against each other
in middle age.

11:09.530 --> 11:10.545
Their own flesh and blood

11:10.940 --> 11:12.185
nearly died in a foreign land.

11:12.490 --> 11:13.330
Later,

11:13.700 --> 11:14.770
exploiting compassion

11:15.180 --> 11:16.130
and a sense of duty,

11:16.370 --> 11:17.770
he bound my father as well.

11:20.300 --> 11:21.340
My poor father.

11:22.370 --> 11:24.770
He longed for the outside world.

11:25.850 --> 11:26.980
Yet in his lifetime,

11:28.530 --> 11:30.820
he never once left the Hanhai Mountains.

11:42.130 --> 11:43.650
Nie Hengcheng is dead.

11:44.850 --> 11:45.690
Zhao,

11:47.180 --> 11:48.020
all of this

11:49.010 --> 11:50.130
will end very soon.

11:54.490 --> 11:55.330
Mu Qingyan.

11:59.650 --> 12:00.490
Young Master,

12:00.650 --> 12:01.690
nothing can happen to you.

12:02.060 --> 12:02.900
If you're gone,

12:02.910 --> 12:03.850
what will we do?

12:03.980 --> 12:05.340
Stop wailing like ghosts.

12:07.610 --> 12:08.450
Qingyan.

12:09.850 --> 12:10.690
Qingyan!

12:11.730 --> 12:12.570
Qingyan.

12:18.370 --> 12:20.010
Why do you treat Qingyan this way?

12:20.250 --> 12:21.130
Did you

12:21.130 --> 12:22.490
really poison him?

12:23.250 --> 12:24.610
I was about to ask you.

12:24.980 --> 12:27.010
He was fine when he attacked
Xuanwu Altar,

12:27.556 --> 12:29.010
yet he was poisoned once you arrived.

12:29.010 --> 12:30.580
I felt sorry for Qingyan.

12:32.370 --> 12:34.770
Why would he be poisoned in your room?

12:34.770 --> 12:35.770
If there were no cause,

12:35.770 --> 12:37.890
why was he in your room at dawn?

12:37.890 --> 12:38.850
What's wrong with that?

12:39.523 --> 12:40.832
We've traveled and lived together

12:40.843 --> 12:41.980
for months.

12:41.980 --> 12:43.490
If I wanted to harm him,

12:43.490 --> 12:44.610
I would've done it long ago.

12:45.180 --> 12:46.396
Why wait until now?

12:46.476 --> 12:47.940
I think you're shifting the suspicion.

12:48.340 --> 12:49.266
Among everyone present,

12:49.650 --> 12:51.100
you're the most suspicious.

12:52.790 --> 12:53.650
Shangguan.

12:53.650 --> 12:54.490
Yes.

12:54.650 --> 12:55.580
Take her out.

12:57.180 --> 12:58.820
Lady Sun, please.

12:58.820 --> 12:59.660
Shangguan,

13:00.130 --> 13:01.610
how dare you treat me like this?

13:03.580 --> 13:04.420
Let go.

13:04.850 --> 13:05.690
Qingyan.

13:06.130 --> 13:06.970
Qingyan.

13:07.340 --> 13:08.180
Qingyan.

13:08.320 --> 13:09.490
- What a surprise.
- Qingyan.

13:09.530 --> 13:10.820
Shangguan is quite formidable.

13:11.123 --> 13:13.309
I need to give him a herbal bath
to dispel the poison.

13:13.940 --> 13:14.780
Let's go.

13:15.060 --> 13:16.220
Mr. Dai, let's go.

13:18.770 --> 13:20.130
Poison changes are unpredictable.

13:21.180 --> 13:22.130
Young Master, take care.

13:24.730 --> 13:26.523
This is a Savior Pill
made by Guangtian Sect.

13:26.820 --> 13:27.700
It may be useful.

13:36.770 --> 13:37.610
She believed it?

13:39.010 --> 13:39.940
She checked the pulse.

13:39.940 --> 13:40.850
You watched the show.

13:41.610 --> 13:42.650
She should believe it now.

13:44.610 --> 13:45.770
How did she poison you?

13:49.010 --> 13:50.420
My father's Fuying Sword.

13:51.060 --> 13:51.900
She knew

13:52.250 --> 13:53.610
I cared most about my father.

13:55.700 --> 13:56.770
But it's fine.

13:58.060 --> 13:59.530
I can use my inner power

13:59.940 --> 14:01.180
to suppress the poison.

14:02.220 --> 14:04.460
She must have acted
under Nie Zhe's orders.

14:12.730 --> 14:13.570
Zhao,

14:15.010 --> 14:15.850
are you willing

14:18.890 --> 14:20.490
to know the real me?

14:28.770 --> 14:29.610
This place

14:30.820 --> 14:32.130
was my only world

14:33.300 --> 14:34.370
before I turned five.

14:36.530 --> 14:37.570
Not long after I was born,

14:38.010 --> 14:39.003
my father was attacked;

14:39.250 --> 14:40.370
his fate was unknown.

14:41.220 --> 14:42.300
When I was one year old,

14:43.180 --> 14:45.010
Nie Zhe, not yet the Chief,

14:45.010 --> 14:46.300
severed my tendons,

14:48.700 --> 14:51.010
forcing Sun Ruoshui to abandon me here.

15:08.730 --> 15:09.650
The child is young.

15:10.060 --> 15:11.650
His limbs will heal soon.

15:12.250 --> 15:13.220
This place is quiet,

15:14.060 --> 15:15.770
free from meddlesome people.

15:26.580 --> 15:27.730
For five whole years,

15:29.220 --> 15:30.490
I had been locked here,

15:31.340 --> 15:32.730
never seeing daylight,

15:34.250 --> 15:36.130
living like a beast.

15:59.850 --> 16:01.940
He doesn't eat like a Young Master.

16:02.180 --> 16:03.130
What a sin.

16:04.130 --> 16:04.970
What do you know?

16:05.100 --> 16:06.700
He's still a Mu.

16:06.700 --> 16:07.766
Killing him would look bad.

16:08.490 --> 16:09.580
With this going on,

16:09.940 --> 16:11.239
he'll be useless sooner or later.

16:31.010 --> 16:31.940
And then?

16:38.370 --> 16:40.010
Later, my father recovered and returned.

16:40.650 --> 16:41.700
When he learned I was here,

16:42.130 --> 16:43.340
he took me back.

17:26.770 --> 17:27.940
My tendons were severed.

17:28.860 --> 17:30.660
My father exhausted his inner power

17:30.660 --> 17:31.940
to rebuild my meridians.

17:33.010 --> 17:33.980
Because of that,

17:34.860 --> 17:35.980
he suffered internal injuries

17:36.730 --> 17:37.860
and a lingering illness.

17:46.860 --> 17:47.770
A few years ago,

17:48.900 --> 17:50.900
my father reached the end of his life

17:51.700 --> 17:53.090
and passed away.

17:54.090 --> 17:55.860
My father's death was suspicious.

17:56.940 --> 17:58.520
Elder Qiu told me how the Nies

17:58.531 --> 18:00.710
(Spirit Tablet of Mu Zhengming)
persecuted my father,

18:00.721 --> 18:02.491
as well as matters
involving my grandfather.

18:05.420 --> 18:06.730
My hatred was unbearable.

18:07.220 --> 18:08.660
I stormed Bliss Palace

18:09.660 --> 18:11.010
to settle accounts with Nie Zhe.

18:42.530 --> 18:44.620
Before, I thought Nie Zhe's Wudu Palm

18:45.290 --> 18:46.490
was poisonous without a cure.

18:47.050 --> 18:47.980
But I did not expect

18:48.266 --> 18:49.906
Nie Zhe's cultivation
to be insufficient.

18:50.220 --> 18:51.420
The Wudu Palm he practices

18:51.770 --> 18:53.180
is not toxic enough to be fatal.

18:54.380 --> 18:55.330
Was it your mother?

18:57.440 --> 18:58.580
It was Nie Zhe.

18:58.770 --> 19:00.220
Knowing that my father and I

19:00.220 --> 19:01.810
both valued the Fuying Sword,

19:02.090 --> 19:04.530
he instructed Sun Ruoshui
to poison the blade.

19:05.220 --> 19:08.090
This time, Nie Zhe wanted
to repeat the trick.

19:08.860 --> 19:11.090
That's how I confirmed my suspicion.

19:11.490 --> 19:13.336
Nie Zhe was certain
you didn't know the truth,

19:13.570 --> 19:15.290
so he poisoned the sword again,

19:15.290 --> 19:17.180
trying to use your mother
to harm you once more.

19:19.700 --> 19:20.700
What a fool.

19:20.980 --> 19:21.820
She's not foolish.

19:23.570 --> 19:24.490
She is arrogant.

19:25.090 --> 19:26.810
My father indulged her in every way.

19:27.860 --> 19:29.290
She thought I was like my father,

19:29.489 --> 19:30.962
someone she could manipulate at will.

19:31.330 --> 19:32.980
So I played along with her plan,

19:32.991 --> 19:34.864
letting her return
to let down Nie Zhe's guard.

19:35.050 --> 19:36.330
After taking Bliss Palace,

19:37.250 --> 19:38.330
how will you deal with her?

19:38.810 --> 19:39.770
I promised my father

19:41.050 --> 19:42.330
to provide for her in old age.

19:43.730 --> 19:45.150
So, I'll provide for her in old age.

19:45.770 --> 19:48.140
After dealing with Nie Zhe
and his followers,

19:48.490 --> 19:51.250
I'll find a clean, comfortable place
for her to live.

19:51.860 --> 19:53.380
She'll live a good life.

19:53.380 --> 19:54.330
No visitors.

19:55.860 --> 19:57.010
She'll grow old in solitude.

19:57.380 --> 19:58.580
Everything happens in circles.

19:58.770 --> 19:59.800
Retribution always comes.

20:00.180 --> 20:01.220
She deserves it.

20:02.900 --> 20:03.980
I'm speaking objectively.

20:04.700 --> 20:05.700
Don't overthink it.

20:05.700 --> 20:06.570
I'm not overthinking.

20:07.530 --> 20:09.220
I just feel that compared to me,

20:09.770 --> 20:11.420
you're more like a demonic sect member.

20:11.420 --> 20:12.886
I'm now an undercover agent

20:12.897 --> 20:14.430
from the Six Sects in the demonic sect.

20:14.570 --> 20:15.900
Naturally, I must act the part.

20:17.980 --> 20:19.140
After dealing with Nie Zhe,

20:20.330 --> 20:21.170
what are your plans?

20:23.010 --> 20:24.570
My father's only regret in life

20:24.980 --> 20:26.730
was never leaving the Hanhai Mountains.

20:27.180 --> 20:29.010
Though I couldn't fulfill his wish,

20:29.520 --> 20:30.860
I still want to follow his intent

20:31.490 --> 20:32.730
and make the Hanhai Mountains

20:32.980 --> 20:35.010
no longer a closed-off place.

20:35.700 --> 20:36.653
To achieve great change,

20:37.076 --> 20:38.339
one must first destroy greatly.

20:38.700 --> 20:39.770
The sect's power

20:40.140 --> 20:41.490
is deeply entangled.

20:41.490 --> 20:42.810
Without absolute strength,

20:42.810 --> 20:44.420
it's hard to win a submission quickly.

20:45.810 --> 20:46.730
I don't have much time.

20:47.090 --> 20:48.180
And I stand alone.

20:49.367 --> 20:50.727
All I can do is gamble everything.

20:51.380 --> 20:52.700
In this situation,

20:53.290 --> 20:54.860
I shouldn't drag you in.

20:55.740 --> 20:56.620
Zhao,

20:56.620 --> 20:57.460
tomorrow morning,

20:57.860 --> 20:59.730
leave with Song Yuzhi.

20:59.730 --> 21:00.570
I came all this way.

21:00.570 --> 21:01.980
How could I leave you alone?

21:02.140 --> 21:03.010
But...

21:03.010 --> 21:03.813
No buts.

21:03.824 --> 21:05.550
At the very least,
we have to kill Nie Zhe.

21:06.010 --> 21:07.180
Right now,

21:07.420 --> 21:09.250
I'm extremely displeased with him too.

21:11.570 --> 21:12.570
You won't regret it?

21:13.602 --> 21:14.896
Why do you talk so much nonsense?

21:16.860 --> 21:17.900
As a businesswoman,

21:18.180 --> 21:19.940
keeping promises matters most.

22:33.900 --> 22:34.740
Honey.

22:42.660 --> 22:43.700
Mr. Nie is unwell.

22:44.180 --> 22:46.290
The Chief has gone to the Lady.

22:49.330 --> 22:50.730
She doesn't deserve to be the Lady.

22:50.940 --> 22:51.880
Lady Sun, spare my life.

22:54.620 --> 22:55.460
Lady Sun...

23:11.290 --> 23:12.980
The Young Lord caught a chill.

23:13.490 --> 23:15.240
Chief, you need not worry.

23:15.380 --> 23:17.090
He must've caught a cold

23:17.090 --> 23:17.980
in the garden that day.

23:23.810 --> 23:25.633
Si'en will one day
take charge of the sect.

23:25.644 --> 23:27.410
He can't stay indoors
studying all the time.

23:27.620 --> 23:29.220
He needs to move around more.

23:29.490 --> 23:30.330
Honey.

23:33.050 --> 23:34.180
You're back so soon.

23:35.290 --> 23:36.250
Mission accomplished.

23:36.700 --> 23:38.660
I heard as soon as I entered

23:38.660 --> 23:39.980
that Si'en was unwell.

23:39.980 --> 23:41.140
I was worried,

23:41.140 --> 23:42.180
so I hurried over to see

23:42.180 --> 23:43.620
if there's anything I can help with.

23:46.180 --> 23:48.620
You needn't put on an act here.

23:49.420 --> 23:51.900
Si'en cannot bear your concern.

23:51.900 --> 23:52.740
You...

23:56.660 --> 23:57.530
Honey...

23:58.010 --> 23:59.140
Since Si'en is fine,

23:59.570 --> 24:00.530
let's go back first.

24:27.940 --> 24:29.126
Dear, thanks for what you did.

24:30.250 --> 24:31.530
This operation went so smoothly,

24:32.290 --> 24:33.770
thanks to your efforts.

24:34.660 --> 24:35.570
Honey, you flatter me.

24:36.010 --> 24:37.180
As your wife,

24:37.180 --> 24:39.770
it is my duty to share your burdens.

24:39.770 --> 24:40.940
As long as you are pleased,

24:41.560 --> 24:42.420
I am

24:42.420 --> 24:43.860
fully content.

24:46.330 --> 24:47.170
Mr. Yu,

24:47.810 --> 24:50.330
reclaim the Qinglong
and Xuanwu Altars asap.

24:50.330 --> 24:52.420
Leave the defense of Bliss Palace
to Fengge.

24:52.770 --> 24:53.770
Understood.

24:55.660 --> 24:56.786
Once Nie Zhe hears the news,

24:57.106 --> 24:58.290
he will surely send Yu Huiyin

24:58.290 --> 25:00.090
to retake the Qinglong
and Xuanwu Altars.

25:00.893 --> 25:02.579
At that point,
the defense of Bliss Palace

25:02.940 --> 25:04.346
can only be entrusted to Hu Fengge.

25:04.490 --> 25:06.730
The red-clad woman
who captured me last time?

25:07.166 --> 25:08.380
Hu Fengge is one of the orphans

25:08.391 --> 25:10.050
Nie Hengcheng took into
the Demonic Camp.

25:10.050 --> 25:12.303
She's known for exceptional talent
and ruthless methods.

25:12.660 --> 25:13.493
After the great war,

25:13.504 --> 25:15.446
Nie Hengcheng's followers
suffered heavy losses.

25:15.770 --> 25:17.810
Hu Fengge was then promoted
to Elder Hufa.

25:18.570 --> 25:20.290
She's always been loyal to Nie Zhe

25:20.660 --> 25:22.220
and devoted to Yu Huiyin.

25:22.770 --> 25:24.250
The remaining Camp elites

25:24.250 --> 25:25.380
are all under her command.

25:25.866 --> 25:27.010
If we clash with her head-on,

25:27.010 --> 25:28.440
there will surely be a bitter battle.

25:28.451 --> 25:29.291
There's no guarantee

25:29.368 --> 25:30.899
Nie Zhe won't seize the chance to flee.

25:30.940 --> 25:32.660
Once Nie Zhe leaves Bliss Palace,

25:32.660 --> 25:34.050
it will be hard to catch him again.

25:34.420 --> 25:35.440
Let's cut off his retreat.

25:35.700 --> 25:36.880
Nail him inside Bliss Palace.

25:39.860 --> 25:40.700
Shangguan,

25:40.900 --> 25:42.490
lead men to Yaoyue Pass with Mr. Song

25:42.490 --> 25:44.900
(Yaoyue Pass)
to draw Hu Fengge away.

25:50.940 --> 25:51.900
Zhao and I will enter

25:52.570 --> 25:54.096
from the back mountain of Bliss Palace.

25:54.256 --> 25:55.638
There are many injured sect members

25:55.649 --> 25:56.900
and villagers in Xuanwu Altar.

25:56.900 --> 25:58.006
The enemy far outnumbers us.

25:58.490 --> 25:59.570
If Yu Huiyin attacks,

25:59.570 --> 26:00.530
how do we respond?

26:00.530 --> 26:01.370
Don't worry.

26:01.540 --> 26:02.993
The Young Master already has a plan.

26:38.180 --> 26:39.140
You Guanyue,

26:39.860 --> 26:41.570
where is your Young Master?

26:41.980 --> 26:42.820
Could it be

26:44.180 --> 26:45.330
that he's already dead?

26:47.290 --> 26:48.130
Why don't you

26:49.330 --> 26:50.530
come in and see

26:51.660 --> 26:52.530
for yourself?

26:53.660 --> 26:55.020
Yu Huiyin is naturally suspicious.

26:55.860 --> 26:57.700
As long as we put on a show,

26:58.220 --> 26:59.570
he will grow wary

27:00.050 --> 27:01.290
and dare not act rashly.

27:03.220 --> 27:04.220
Nie Zhe's end

27:05.620 --> 27:07.050
should also be shown to my father.

27:29.050 --> 27:29.890
Traitor!

27:40.330 --> 27:41.170
Let's go.

28:03.980 --> 28:04.860
Xuanwu Altar

28:05.570 --> 28:06.810
isn't a place you can enter

28:07.220 --> 28:08.380
just because you want to.

28:30.050 --> 28:31.010
Come in, then.

28:34.140 --> 28:34.980
Something's wrong.

28:35.140 --> 28:35.980
Guards.

28:36.380 --> 28:37.220
Yes.

28:37.980 --> 28:39.186
Hurry and notify Bliss Palace.

28:39.420 --> 28:40.693
Tell them to stay on high alert.

28:40.860 --> 28:41.700
Yes.

28:48.660 --> 28:50.380
Your contribution is outstanding.

28:50.660 --> 28:52.570
You're worthy of being my wife.

28:53.050 --> 28:54.700
After we finish the Mu clan remnants,

28:55.330 --> 28:57.050
we shall hold the investiture ceremony.

28:58.810 --> 28:59.810
Thank you, Chief.

29:07.940 --> 29:08.780
Actually,

29:09.250 --> 29:11.380
as long as I can stay by your side,

29:12.250 --> 29:14.010
I will be fully content.

29:20.250 --> 29:21.140
It's getting late.

29:21.980 --> 29:23.290
Si'en needs to rest.

29:24.250 --> 29:26.380
Why do you look unhappy?

29:29.420 --> 29:30.873
Fellow disciples fighting each other.

29:31.330 --> 29:32.730
What is there to be happy about?

29:35.980 --> 29:37.010
Are you dissatisfied

29:37.010 --> 29:39.490
with the Chief?

29:39.940 --> 29:42.330
When my foster father was still alive,

29:42.660 --> 29:44.530
we often drank wine in this hall.

29:44.810 --> 29:47.380
Lu and Han would dance
with swords for amusement.

29:47.810 --> 29:49.380
If Mr. Mu Zhengming came,

29:49.730 --> 29:51.180
he'd play music in accompaniment.

29:51.770 --> 29:53.250
Back then, the sect prospered.

29:53.620 --> 29:54.573
Everyone was still here.

29:55.090 --> 29:56.530
There was no rebellion to suppress

29:58.010 --> 29:59.010
and certainly no

30:00.010 --> 30:01.570
shamelessness,

30:01.570 --> 30:03.050
no disregard for moral bonds.

30:08.250 --> 30:09.940
That's not right.

30:10.810 --> 30:12.010
Are you saying

30:12.380 --> 30:14.900
the Chief is inferior
to the former chief?

30:15.660 --> 30:17.380
After the former chief passed away,

30:17.380 --> 30:19.530
the sect nearly fell apart.

30:19.530 --> 30:20.770
If not for the Chief

30:20.770 --> 30:22.660
turning the tide and restoring order,

30:23.080 --> 30:23.940
how would the sect

30:23.940 --> 30:26.660
enjoy today's prosperity and stability?

30:27.256 --> 30:29.330
What right do you have
to speak of the former chief?

30:29.330 --> 30:30.783
If my foster father were still alive,

30:31.090 --> 30:34.220
how could he tolerate
a treacherous person like you?

30:35.330 --> 30:36.170
You...

30:37.380 --> 30:38.220
Enough.

30:39.860 --> 30:40.810
Ruxin,

30:40.810 --> 30:42.010
since Si'en is sleepy,

30:42.770 --> 30:44.090
take him back to rest.

30:51.730 --> 30:52.570
Let's go.

30:59.940 --> 31:00.900
Chief,

31:02.700 --> 31:04.420
look at Ruxin...

31:05.980 --> 31:07.980
Servants, remove all of this.

31:09.090 --> 31:09.930
Yes,

31:10.290 --> 31:11.130
Chief.

31:32.900 --> 31:34.010
You're not dead.

31:36.660 --> 31:37.620
Uncle Nie.

31:38.980 --> 31:39.820
Qingyan.

31:41.490 --> 31:42.330
Lady Sun,

31:42.330 --> 31:44.220
I didn't promise to spare your life.

31:44.620 --> 31:45.530
I advise you

31:45.810 --> 31:47.330
to mind your words and actions

31:47.330 --> 31:48.420
and stop meddling.

31:48.860 --> 31:49.900
Mu Qingyan,

31:50.810 --> 31:52.140
what do you mean by this?

31:52.140 --> 31:53.900
The capable rule the sect.

31:54.730 --> 31:56.010
I wish to face you

31:56.570 --> 31:57.900
in another duel.

31:59.900 --> 32:00.860
Have you forgotten?

32:01.620 --> 32:03.620
You already lost two years ago.

32:03.620 --> 32:06.180
You also ate two years ago.
Why still eat today?

32:06.180 --> 32:07.900
Besides, you poisoned him last time

32:07.900 --> 32:09.250
and won without honor.

32:10.140 --> 32:11.900
Even if you had won by strength,

32:12.570 --> 32:14.570
does that mean
he can't challenge you again?

32:14.570 --> 32:15.410
Mu Qingyan,

32:15.770 --> 32:18.050
you sneaked into Bliss Palace

32:18.050 --> 32:20.490
and let this demoness
spout nonsense here.

32:21.180 --> 32:22.940
Are you planning to betray the sect?

32:22.940 --> 32:24.186
The sect belongs to the Mu clan.

32:24.860 --> 32:25.933
How can this be betrayal?

32:26.490 --> 32:27.330
What?

32:27.570 --> 32:28.810
Are you afraid?

32:41.940 --> 32:42.860
Shangguan,

32:42.860 --> 32:43.730
you traitor.

32:44.140 --> 32:46.530
Elders Kaiyang and Yaoguang took you in.

32:47.380 --> 32:49.700
They were loyal to the former chief.

32:49.700 --> 32:50.793
Yet you switched allegiance

32:50.804 --> 32:51.770
and betrayed the sect.

32:52.700 --> 32:53.940
Elder Hu, that's not right.

32:54.330 --> 32:56.620
From beginning to end,
I have only been loyal to Mr. Mu.

32:56.620 --> 32:57.603
I have never changed.

32:57.614 --> 32:59.127
Why accuse me of switching allegiance?

32:59.420 --> 33:00.495
Back then, the two elders

33:00.506 --> 33:02.180
wholeheartedly followed Nie Hengcheng.

33:02.570 --> 33:03.643
They died without regret.

33:03.980 --> 33:05.140
Today, I do the same.

33:05.420 --> 33:07.250
You've always been Mu Qingyan's spy.

33:07.810 --> 33:08.650
You deserve death.

33:09.980 --> 33:10.820
(The summons.)

33:10.976 --> 33:12.416
(Something's wrong at Bliss Palace.)

33:19.570 --> 33:20.490
What's going on?

33:20.730 --> 33:21.570
Numbing Powder.

33:22.290 --> 33:24.250
You're a righteous sect member,

33:24.570 --> 33:25.810
yet you play such petty tricks?

33:25.900 --> 33:26.940
Necessity knows no rules.

33:27.353 --> 33:28.859
A gentleman need not cling to trifles.

33:31.090 --> 33:32.620
Victory matters more than origins.

33:33.810 --> 33:35.130
Moves need not follow convention.

33:36.180 --> 33:37.020
New knowledge.

34:09.050 --> 34:11.010
Your cultivation improved so soon.

34:11.570 --> 34:13.010
What have you practiced?

34:13.260 --> 34:14.260
You've lost.

34:14.690 --> 34:15.570
Uncle Nie,

34:16.530 --> 34:17.380
step down.

34:29.380 --> 34:31.010
Powder ground from Qianxun Wood.

34:32.530 --> 34:33.740
It's said Qianxun Wood

34:33.740 --> 34:35.570
can catalyze the poison
of Suzi Fragrance.

34:39.050 --> 34:41.740
So, the poison you used on him
was Suzi Fragrance.

34:47.380 --> 34:48.340
Hand over the antidote.

34:48.980 --> 34:49.846
What antidote?

34:49.857 --> 34:51.077
The antidote to Suzi Fragrance.

34:52.570 --> 34:54.523
Mr. Mu originally thought
the poison he suffered

34:54.534 --> 34:55.530
was from the Wudu Palm.

34:56.300 --> 34:57.530
He never expected

34:57.530 --> 35:00.090
the truly lethal poison to be...

35:02.300 --> 35:03.420
So what?

35:05.340 --> 35:07.050
You're sharp as a fox.

35:07.860 --> 35:09.940
How could ordinary poisons fool you?

35:10.170 --> 35:12.130
Suzi Fragrance is colorless
and odorless.

35:13.090 --> 35:15.690
I meant to let it slowly
consume you to death.

35:17.610 --> 35:19.650
Once mixed with Qianxun Wood,

35:19.650 --> 35:21.090
it becomes deadly poison.

35:21.860 --> 35:23.420
There is no cure in the world.

35:24.490 --> 35:25.330
Mu Qingyan,

35:25.780 --> 35:27.210
so what if you won?

35:28.900 --> 35:31.420
Even your mother wants you dead.

35:32.210 --> 35:33.530
Your mother tried to kill you.

35:34.090 --> 35:36.980
Your father also died unnaturally
because of you.

35:37.420 --> 35:39.860
What right do you have
to live in this world?

35:43.260 --> 35:44.130
My father...

35:46.300 --> 35:47.820
How exactly did he die?

35:53.740 --> 35:55.740
After years of being consumed
by Suzi Fragrance,

35:56.570 --> 35:58.300
the poison flared, and he died.

36:17.490 --> 36:19.300
So, you did kill him...

36:27.170 --> 36:28.010
Don't listen to them.

36:45.260 --> 36:47.130
This cage is made of refined dark iron.

36:47.690 --> 36:48.820
You cannot break it.

36:49.570 --> 36:50.570
There will no longer be

36:51.010 --> 36:52.210
a Mu clan in this world.

36:52.210 --> 36:53.940
Nie Zhe, you shameless jerk.

36:53.940 --> 36:55.380
How could you resort to dirty tricks?

36:55.380 --> 36:57.170
Stop your futile struggle.

36:57.170 --> 36:59.980
Soon, you'll become piles
of white bones.

37:09.170 --> 37:10.050
Erosion Ants.

37:10.300 --> 37:12.170
A paired mother-and-child Gu

37:12.420 --> 37:13.420
recorded in strange lore.

37:13.420 --> 37:14.610
They feed on flesh and blood

37:15.090 --> 37:16.260
and reproduce rapidly.

37:17.980 --> 37:18.900
They're getting closer.

37:18.980 --> 37:19.820
Use your inner power.

37:25.860 --> 37:26.860
Don't waste your effort.

37:27.340 --> 37:28.380
Just wait for death.

37:29.050 --> 37:29.890
Nie Zhe!

37:36.170 --> 37:37.743
The child ants must sense the mother ant

37:37.754 --> 37:38.740
to receive commands.

37:38.740 --> 37:40.260
The one controlling the ants

37:40.260 --> 37:41.380
must be nearby.

37:45.170 --> 37:46.340
At a time like this,

37:47.530 --> 37:48.650
why not come out?

37:49.260 --> 37:51.050
If you can't witness
our miserable deaths,

37:51.780 --> 37:53.650
wouldn't all your scheming be in vain?

37:54.090 --> 37:55.530
You know who's behind this?

37:55.940 --> 37:56.940
I miscalculated.

37:57.363 --> 37:59.509
I didn't expect
that among Nie Hengcheng's disciples,

37:59.900 --> 38:01.530
one would still be alive.

38:02.420 --> 38:03.900
If I'm not mistaken,

38:05.340 --> 38:07.050
it must be Han Yisu,

38:07.050 --> 38:08.170
Elder Han, right?

38:14.920 --> 38:25.580
=Generation to Generation=

38:44.340 --> 38:48.750
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

38:49.315 --> 38:53.930
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

38:54.270 --> 38:58.835
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

38:59.360 --> 39:03.660
♪Free to wander in the world♪

39:06.605 --> 39:11.305
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:11.830 --> 39:16.120
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

39:16.780 --> 39:20.810
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

39:21.125 --> 39:26.250
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

39:26.825 --> 39:31.635
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:31.850 --> 39:36.020
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:36.745 --> 39:40.680
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:41.180 --> 39:46.455
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

40:09.185 --> 40:14.315
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:14.680 --> 40:19.050
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

40:19.315 --> 40:23.445
♪I freely roam in the world♪

40:23.630 --> 40:29.205
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
